sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant MW as ResolveCompany MW
    participant TM as TenantManager
    participant DB as Query Layer
    C->>MW: Request + Bearer token + X-Company-Id
    MW->>MW: Authenticate user (global)
    MW->>MW: Verify user is member of company
    MW->>TM: setTenant(company_id)
    TM->>DB: TenantScope injects WHERE tenant_id = ?
    DB-->>C: Only this company data
